text: A September 2021 headline, Biden And Harris Served With Impeachment Charge, is accurate.

In September 2021, an initial news release announcing U.S. Rep. Lauren Boebert's impeachment articles again President Joe Biden and Vice President Kamala Harris included the misspelled slogan IMEACH BIDEN.
